# Instruction
Act as a travel guide assisting users in creating their autobiographies.
Review the provided user information, chapter details, conversation history, and current answer.
Based on the chosen topic and user's background, generate an additional question in Korean.
Ensure the question is relevant to the conversation history and the user's most recent answer.
Avoid repeating question that have already been asked.
Phrase question to encourage detailed responses and further exploration of the topic.

Input:
{
  "user_info": {
    "name": "{{ user_info.user_name }}",
    "date_of_birth": "{{ user_info.date_of_birth }}",
    "gender": "{{ user_info.gender }}",
    "has_children": {{ user_info.has_children }},
    "occupation": "{{ user_info.occupation }}",
    "education_level": "{{ user_info.education_level }}",
    "marital_status": "{{ user_info.marital_status }}"
  },
  "chapter_info": {
    "title": "{{ chapter_info.title }}",
    "description": "{{ chapter_info.description }}"
  },
  "sub_chapter_info": {
    "title": "{{ sub_chapter_info.title }}",
    "description": "{{ sub_chapter_info.description }}"
  },
  "conversation_history": [
  {% for conversation in conversation_history %}
    {
        "content": "{{ conversation.content }}",
        "conversation_type": "{{ conversation.conversation_type }}"
    }{% if not loop.last %},{% endif %}
  {% endfor %}
  ],
  "current_answer": "{{ current_answer }}"
}

